@startuml user-state
title User Account State Diagram

[*] --> REGISTERED : User completes\nregistration form\n/ email sent

REGISTERED --> ACTIVE_BUYER : Email verified\n/ role = BUYER

REGISTERED --> PENDING_VERIFICATION : Email verified\n/ role = SELLER

PENDING_VERIFICATION --> ACTIVE_SELLER : Admin approves\nseller verification\n/ documents valid

PENDING_VERIFICATION --> VERIFICATION_REJECTED : Admin rejects\nverification\n/ reason provided

VERIFICATION_REJECTED --> PENDING_VERIFICATION : Seller resubmits\nupdated documents

ACTIVE_BUYER --> ACTIVE_SELLER : Buyer requests\nseller upgrade\n/ submits documents

ACTIVE_SELLER --> ACTIVE_BUYER : Seller downgrades\nor loses seller status

ACTIVE_BUYER --> SUSPENDED : Admin suspends\naccount\n(policy violation)

ACTIVE_SELLER --> SUSPENDED : Admin suspends\naccount\n(policy violation /\nnegative reviews)

SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE_BUYER : Admin reinstates\nbuyer account

SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE_SELLER : Admin reinstates\nseller account

SUSPENDED --> BANNED : Repeated\nviolations\n/ admin bans

ACTIVE_BUYER --> DEACTIVATED : User requests\naccount deletion

ACTIVE_SELLER --> DEACTIVATED : User requests\naccount deletion\n[no open auctions]

DEACTIVATED --> ACTIVE_BUYER : User reactivates\nwithin grace period

BANNED --> [*] : Account permanently\nremoved

DEACTIVATED --> [*] : Grace period\nexpires, data\npurged

note right of PENDING_VERIFICATION
  Seller must submit:
  - Student ID
  - Hostel room proof
  Admin reviews within 48h.
end note

note right of SUSPENDED
  Suspended users cannot
  bid, create auctions,
  or make payments.
  Existing escrow frozen.
end note

@enduml
